*PPD-Adobe: "4.3"
*%PPD file for QuadToneRIP with ESC/P-Raster Driver
*%Custom PPD for EPSON SC-P9550 with ESC/P-Raster Protocol
*%Inks K,C,M,Y,LC,LM,LK,LLK,OR,GR
*FormatVersion: "4.3"
*FileVersion: "1.0"
*LanguageVersion: English
*LanguageEncoding: ISOLatin1
*PCFileName: "P9550_ESCPR_QTR.PPD"
*Product: "(EPSON SC-P9550 Series ESC/P-Raster)"
*PSVersion: "(3011.106) 0"
*ModelName: "EPSON SC-P9550 QTR ESC/P-R"
*ShortNickName: "P9550 QTR ESC/P-R"
*NickName: "EPSON SC-P9550 QuadToneRIP ESC/P-Raster"
*Manufacturer: "EPSON"
*LanguageLevel: "3"
*ColorDevice: True
*DefaultColorSpace: Gray
*cupsSNMPSupplies: False
*cupsIPPSupplies: False
*FileSystem: False
*Throughput: "1"
*TTRasterizer: Type42

*cupsVersion: 1.7
*cupsManualCopies: False
*cupsModelNumber: 1

*% Custom CUPS filter chain for ESC/P-Raster with QuadToneRIP
*% Step 1: Convert PostScript/PDF to CUPS Raster (using system filter)
*cupsFilter2: "application/vnd.cups-postscript application/vnd.cups-raster 100 cgpdftoraster"
*% Step 2: Convert CUPS Raster to ESC/P-Raster with QuadToneRIP curves
*cupsFilter: "application/vnd.cups-raster 0 /Library/Printers/QTR/filter/rastertop9550"

*% Paper sizes
*OpenUI *PageSize: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PageSize
*DefaultPageSize: A4
*PageSize Letter/Letter: "<</PageSize[612 792]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize A4/A4: "<</PageSize[595 842]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize A3/A3: "<</PageSize[842 1191]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize A3+/A3+: "<</PageSize[932 1369]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize B/B (11x17): "<</PageSize[792 1224]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize SuperB/Super B (13x19): "<</PageSize[936 1368]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize 4x6/4x6 in: "<</PageSize[288 432]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize 5x7/5x7 in: "<</PageSize[360 504]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageSize 8x10/8x10 in: "<</PageSize[576 720]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PageSize

*OpenUI *PageRegion: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *PageRegion
*DefaultPageRegion: A4
*PageRegion Letter/Letter: "<</PageSize[612 792]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion A4/A4: "<</PageSize[595 842]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion A3/A3: "<</PageSize[842 1191]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion A3+/A3+: "<</PageSize[932 1369]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion B/B (11x17): "<</PageSize[792 1224]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion SuperB/Super B (13x19): "<</PageSize[936 1368]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion 4x6/4x6 in: "<</PageSize[288 432]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion 5x7/5x7 in: "<</PageSize[360 504]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion 8x10/8x10 in: "<</PageSize[576 720]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PageRegion

*DefaultImageableArea: A4
*ImageableArea Letter/Letter: "18 18 594 774"
*ImageableArea A4/A4: "18 18 577 824"
*ImageableArea A3/A3: "18 18 824 1173"
*ImageableArea A3+/A3+: "18 18 914 1351"
