*% Resolution
*OpenUI *Resolution/Resolution: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 15 AnySetup *Resolution
*DefaultResolution: 720dpi
*Resolution 360dpi/360 DPI: "<</HWResolution[360 360]>>setpagedevice"
*Resolution 720dpi/720 DPI: "<</HWResolution[720 720]>>setpagedevice"
*Resolution 1440dpi/1440 DPI: "<</HWResolution[1440 1440]>>setpagedevice"
*Resolution 2880dpi/2880 DPI: "<</HWResolution[2880 2880]>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Resolution

*% Media Type
*OpenUI *MediaType/Media Type: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 16 AnySetup *MediaType
*DefaultMediaType: PlainPaper
*MediaType PlainPaper/Plain Paper: ""
*MediaType PhotoPaper/Photo Paper: ""
*MediaType MattePaper/Matte Paper: ""
*MediaType Glossy/Glossy Photo Paper: ""
*MediaType FineArt/Fine Art Paper: ""
*MediaType Canvas/Canvas: ""
*MediaType Baryta/Baryta Paper: ""
*CloseUI: *MediaType

*% QuadToneRIP Curve Selection
*OpenUI *ripCurve1/QuadTone RIP Curve 1: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 20 AnySetup *ripCurve1
*DefaultripCurve1: P9550-PtPd-xf1-3ink
*ripCurve1 -/None (Linear): ""
*ripCurve1 P9550-PtPd-xf1-3ink/P9550 PtPd xf1 3ink: ""
*CloseUI: *ripCurve1

*% Color model
*OpenUI *ColorModel/Color Mode: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *ColorModel
*DefaultColorModel: Gray
*ColorModel Gray/Grayscale: "<</cupsColorSpace 18/cupsColorOrder 0/cupsBitsPerColor 8>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *ColorModel

*% Duplex
*OpenUI *Duplex/Duplex: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *Duplex
*DefaultDuplex: None
*Duplex None/Off: "<</Duplex false>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *Duplex

*% Input slot
*OpenUI *InputSlot/Paper Source: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 10 AnySetup *InputSlot
*DefaultInputSlot: AutoSelect
*InputSlot AutoSelect/Auto Select: ""
*InputSlot Roll/Roll Paper: ""
*InputSlot Sheet/Sheet: ""
*CloseUI: *InputSlot

